snippet.title: Rotato trailer
snippet.description:
Rotato is a simple but challenging puzzle game. Rotate the blocks to match the shapes. The game has over 200 hand designed levels and a custom mode with infinite random levels.

Play it for free at at: https://sybrial.itch.io/

Get it on google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sybrial.rotato.android
